description: One of the peaks around the Titlis

I have seen sooo many pictures of those beautiful Icelandic horses online that of course I also need to take a few. My expectation was the typical picture with the wind blowing through the hair of a horse, but after winning the trust of the horses they allowed me to take this lovely photo. I am still not finished editing all my Iceland pictures. So here is another bunch of goodies from my latest trip!
